msgid "``ABSOLUTE_PATH``"
msgstr "``ABSOLUTE_PATH``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rastermiscellaneous.rst:1407
msgid ""
"Set whether the absolute path to the raster files is stored in the tile "
"index file. By default the raster filenames will be put in the file exactly "
"as they are specified in the command."
msgstr ""
"Ställ in om den absoluta sökvägen till rasterfilerna ska lagras i filen för "
"kakelindex. Som standard kommer rasterfilnamnen att läggas in i filen exakt "
"som de anges i kommandot."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rastermiscellaneous.rst:1411
msgid "**Skip files with different projection reference**"
msgstr "**Skippa filer med annan projektionsreferens**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rastermiscellaneous.rst:1416
msgid ""
"Only files with same projection as files already inserted in the tile index "
"will be inserted. Default does not check projection and accepts all inputs."
msgstr ""
"Endast filer med samma projektion som filer som redan är infogade i "
"kakelindexet kommer att infogas. Standard kontrollerar inte projektion och "
"accepterar alla inmatningar."

